{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A quirky cooperative puzzle game that can be played with friends and online players. Fluffy cube-shaped creatures team up to solve puzzles together!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Local and Online Co-op Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ring the bell</strong> in the lobby to match with other players online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Bell_EN_02.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play locally or create a <strong>party code</strong> with the TV in the lobby, so <strong>friends can join you</strong> online. Play in any combination e.g. two local players and two online players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/TV_EN_02.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Duo Mode</strong> allows you to control 2 creatures from 1 controller. Share the controller with a friend to use half each or test your skills to control both yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Tips_Pair_Mode.png?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Helping Each Other is Key, for All Ages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With <strong>intuitive and simple controls</strong>, anyone can jump into the game right away. Since you can\u2019t rotate, solving puzzles always requires the help of your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Puzzle_Both.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>160 Diverse Stages, Including Special Stages</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stages usually require all players to work together but every now and then a <strong>special 2v2 stage</strong> appears!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Soccer_02.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Spin the gacha to get stamps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use coins to spin the gacha. <strong>Collect stamps</strong> and unlock accessories and furniture. Once you\u2019ve collected enough stamps you\u2019ll unlock new items and <strong>stage themes</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/StampCard_en.png?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customize with Accessories, Skins and Furniture</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Change the furniture to create your own <strong>unique room</strong>, also change your character's skin and accessories to <strong>suit your style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Skin_EN_02.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fun Voice Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple controls, the creatures will <strong>say various phrases</strong> depending on the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/extras/Snow_EN_02.gif?t=1734584546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Yarnyard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/d5e0a2bc2a271eb72fa57e93d3f6ca2c8eb76d1a.jpg"},{"name":"Keep Moving Forward!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/47e157c23b4c1d26f5095fdbe76f8ffc0a47eb10.jpg"},{"name":"My First Big Gacha Adventure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/d4af1d91a17ba32b47cd14b9519b2618bbea2b4a.jpg"},{"name":"Can't Stop the Gacha!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/17f16068a734ef55e8d6f383bf22ff80335ae4e3.jpg"},{"name":"Soft Spotted","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/6645f990d90d3a31677308f08a69464d04481ba8.jpg"},{"name":"Heartfelt Praise","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/171a75366934186a3f79faeae37fc64e202182cb.jpg"},{"name":"Stuff of Love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/57e6ec9e58eed90d238a8c6fe720861c93dba175.jpg"},{"name":"Nice Play!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/4a286768bb11a3a40d9e5fe6b7ae370767a20666.jpg"},{"name":"That's How It's Done!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/ecac3aeca6bfab2c615c97b2c637bd52e0070bc6.jpg"},{"name":"Everyone's Teacher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2249590/030347fc42ad257cd3e77c6eb8f74b1a18cf5d65.jpg"}],"total":31},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734584546","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a